OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FUnsettled on Thursday with a band of
OL,7,Fheavy rain pushing southwards. Feeling
OL,8,Fcolder on Friday with blustery
OL,9,Fshowers, wintry over hills in the
OL,10,Fnorth. Drier on Saturday with fewer
OL,11,Fshowers.
